gate: LOCKED
v:4 role:dev x:nextjs-tailwind
task: S03 T3 — #650 Catalog-card add-to-cart missing imageUrl
requires: [NEXTJS_VERCEL_FRONTEND]
sprint: S03
repos: [crop-front]
branch: issue-650

context: |
  Cart line items added from the catalog grid/list card show no image (placeholder)
  while the PDP and the catalog card itself both show the real image.
  Root cause (audit-confirmed against dev):
  - features/catalog/product-card-add-to-cart.tsx:44-52 builds the cart item payload
    WITHOUT imageUrl, even though part.media.primaryImage is available on the card.
  - app/cart/_components/cart-item-card.tsx:144-176 renders item.imageUrl correctly
    when present, MediaPlaceholder when absent.
  - PDP add-to-cart (product-purchase-panel.tsx:131) DOES pass imageUrl — working fine.
  - PR #840 only swapped placeholder branding; the data gap is untouched.
  This is NOT the same bug as #827 (RecentlyViewed store schema — different code path).

steps:
  1. Branch: git checkout -b issue-650 dev
  2. Before fix — repro artifact:
     - Open https://crop.clintontractor.net/parts on prod
     - Find any part card with a real image (not placeholder)
     - Click "Add to cart" on the CARD (not the title link)
     - Open the cart → screenshot the placeholder in the cart line
     - Post part number + screenshot as a comment on issue #650
  3. Fix: features/catalog/product-card-add-to-cart.tsx
     In the addItem() call payload, add: imageUrl: part.media.primaryImage
     While there, audit for other fields the PDP payload includes but the card
     payload omits (check product-purchase-panel.tsx:132-140 for the full PDP payload):
     availability, stockCount, shippingPath — add any that are missing and available.
  4. Unit test: assert addItem is called with imageUrl: part.media.primaryImage
     when the part has an image, and imageUrl: undefined when it doesn't.
     File: features/catalog/product-card-add-to-cart.test.tsx (co-locate with source)
  5. Regression: verify PDP add-to-cart still passes imageUrl (product-purchase-panel test).
  6. Commit: fix(catalog): pass imageUrl in catalog-card add-to-cart payload (#650)
  7. Open draft PR into dev, reference #650, include before/after screenshots.

cmd:
  - bun run lint:fix
  - bun run type-check
  - bunx vitest run features/catalog/product-card-add-to-cart.test.tsx

out:
  - features/catalog/product-card-add-to-cart.tsx (imageUrl + any missing fields added)
  - features/catalog/product-card-add-to-cart.test.tsx (new unit test)
  - issue #650 comment with before repro artifact

done:
  - Catalog card add → cart shows real image (verified on Vercel preview)
  - PDP add → cart still shows real image (regression green)
  - vitest passes for the new unit test
  - lint + type-check clean
  - PR draft open against dev
